NK003(ga)017:0: dri med rnam gnyis kyi mchod rten bzhengs skabs nyer
NK003(ga)017:1: mkho'i zin bris gzhan phan zla snang zhes bya ba
NK003(ga)017:3: thugs rje'i zla zer gang du snang tsam gyis //
NK003(ga)017:4: snyigs dus rgud pa'i mun pa rab bsal nas //
NK003(ga)017:5: phan bde'i dbugs 'byin stsol mdzad bcom ldan 'das //
NK003(ga)017:6: bla ma thub pa'i dbang pos dge legs stsol //
NK003(ga)017:7: ston pa thugs rje can gyis grol ba bzhi ldan
NK003(ga)017:8: gyi phrin las mngon gsum gzugs su snang ba dri
NK003(ga)017:9: med rnam gnyis kyi mchod rten bzhengs par 'dod pa'i
NK003(ga)017:10: lhag bsam can dag gis 'di ltar nges par bya
NK003(ga)017:11: ste / spyir mchod rten che chung gang yin yang
NK003(ga)017:12: dri med rnam gnyis kyi cho gas bsgrubs pa zhig
NK003(ga)017:13: byung na sa rdo las bcos kyang 'brel tshad don
NK003(ga)017:14: ldan byas pa don yod du 'gyur /
NK003(ga)017:15: de ltar ma yin na gser dngul las bcos pa'ang rten phal pa tsam las mi 'byung bas /
NK003(ga)017:16: de'i sger chos lo chen rin po che'i cho ga sgrigs bklags pas grub pa ltar /
NK003(ga)017:17: thog mar slob dpon gyis bsnyen par bya dgos pas bsnyen tshad rab gzungs ring khri bzhi /
NK003(ga)017:19: de ltar ma grub na gzungs ring khri dang snying po 'bum bzlas /
NK003(ga)017:20: bzlas pa'i skabs su khrus dang /
NK003(ga)017:22: dkar spyad sogs kun spyod shin tu zhib pa dang /
NK003(ga)017:23: thun mtshams su mdo sdud dang sher snying sogs sher mdo gang rung bklag /
NK003(ga)017:24: bsnyen pa grub nas 'od zer dri med kyi s+aats+tsha dgu bcu go dgu ser po /
NK003(ga)017:25: gtsug tor dri med brgya dang brgyad dkar po rnams
NK003(ga)017:26: cho ga dang ldan par btab cing so so'i gzungs
NK003(ga)017:27: ring ngam / s+aats+tsha chung ngu la mi shong na
NK003(ga)017:28: gzungs thung nang gzhug btsud pa mkhan po'i lugs kyi
NK003(ga)017:29: cho ga rgyas bsdus gang rung gis tshul bzhin bsgrubs
NK003(ga)017:30: ring ngam / / sats+tsha mang po 'grub kyang legs /
NK003(ga)017:31: de nas sa chog la mchod rten dngos sam khang
NK003(ga)017:32: bu brtsegs pa gang rung bzhengs pa'i sa gzhir phyin
NK003(ga)017:33: la cho ga gzhung gsal ltar dang /
NK003(ga)017:34: seng ldeng phur bu brgyad dngos su 'byor dgos /
NK003(ga)017:35: rin po che'i gter bcug pa'i skabs dbus dang phyogs mtshams gang 'dzom du /
NK003(ga)017:38: dbus ma'i mdun du sa bdag bum pa rdo sgrom sogs lag tshags dam par bya /
NK003(ga)017:40: de'i steng du sngar gyi phur pa btab skabs phyogs
NK003(ga)017:41: mtshams rdo sgrom lta bus mi rul ba'i thabs dang
NK003(ga)017:42: bcas te gzhug / 'di skabs grub na rang ngam /
NK003(ga)017:43: grogs kyis bsang dang gser skyems /
NK003(ga)017:44: sa bdag 'khrugs bcos sogs kyang bgyis na legs /
NK003(ga)017:45: de nas khang brtsegs yin na /
NK003(ga)017:46: rmang gi bang rim gnyis brtsegs nas dbus dkyil 'khor gyi 'go thad du nor bum dang /
NK003(ga)017:47: gnod sbyin 'khor lo sogs yod na rang rang gi cho ga ltar sba /
NK003(ga)017:48: khang pa'i steng thog bar legs par brtsigs te btab /
NK003(ga)017:49: mchod rten yin na bum rten bar brtsegs la gnod
NK003(ga)017:50: sbyin bang mdzod kyi ka ca sogs spyi ltar bya
NK003(ga)017:51: / gang ltar yang 'og gzhi zhal ba legs par
NK003(ga)017:52: byas pa'i dbus su khru do las mi chung ba'i
NK003(ga)017:54: de nas gtsug tor dri med kyi dkyil 'khor rdul
NK003(ga)017:55: tshon gyis bris na legs kyang zub pa sogs kyis
NK003(ga)017:57: stabs bder rdo leb la brkos nas tshon legs par byugs par pra rtsi btang ba bshams /
NK003(ga)017:58: dkyil 'khor gyi steng du bla bre sngon po phub /
NK003(ga)017:59: mthar byang shar nas brtsams mtshams 'dzin gyi me tog
NK003(ga)017:60: dang chu gnyis sngon 'gro'i nyer spyod de spyi mchod
NK003(ga)017:61: dang / de'i phyi rol du sgos mchod rnam lnga
NK003(ga)017:62: shar du lhag gcig dang bcas pa'i phyogs rer drug
NK003(ga)017:63: dang / re bsham / cis kyang ma 'byor na
NK003(ga)017:64: shar du lhag gcig dang bcas pa'i re re med
NK003(ga)017:65: dang / re bsham / thabs med / de rnams kyang gtan du bzhag dgos pas /
NK003(ga)017:66: snod kyi rigs 'byor na li sogs dang /
NK003(ga)017:68: mchod yon gyi snod du lan tsh+wa bzang po blugs /
NK003(ga)017:69: de steng rdzas bdun gyis bkang /
NK003(ga)017:70: rdzas bdun ni tsam pa ka dang /
NK003(ga)017:71: ba lu'i me tog lta bu'i me tog dkar po gang 'byor /
NK003(ga)017:77: 6 'o ma 7skabs 'dir rul nyen gyis phyur ba blugs /
NK003(ga)017:78: zhabs bsil la lan tsh+wa'i steng shun pa lnga dang /
NK003(ga)017:79: 'dag rdzas rigs kyi phye mas bkang /
NK003(ga)017:80: shun pa lnga dngos bod du mi 'byor yang /
NK003(ga)017:81: sngon gyi bla ma rnams kyi phyag bzhed du /
NK003(ga)017:85: 'am bu rnams kyi bar shun dang /
NK003(ga)017:86: tsan+dana dkar po bcas kyis tshar rung mdzad tshul yod /
NK003(ga)017:90: 'bras spu bcad pa'i shun pa'i phye ma sogs sbyar /
NK003(ga)017:91: me tog ni 'byor na gos chen sogs kyis bcos pa dang ma 'byor na 'bru dkar /
NK003(ga)017:92: bdug spos spos reng spos ta la btsugs /
NK003(ga)017:93: mar me rdza kong lta bu gtan du bzhag lo ba dgos /
NK003(ga)017:94: dri chab lan tsh+wa'i steng gur gum /
NK003(ga)017:98: tsan+dana dkar po ste dri lnga'i phye mas bkang /
NK003(ga)017:99: zhal zas mar zan lta bu las bzhengs /
NK003(ga)017:100: de'i phyi rol du cod pan nam dar dpyang /
NK003(ga)017:103: gdugs rnams gos dar sogs las bcos pa phyogs rer
NK003(ga)017:104: brgyad re'am ma mtha' re re rdza yi spos 'dzin
NK003(ga)017:106: de'i phyi rol du yol ba dmar pos zlum bskor bya /
NK003(ga)017:107: de'i phyi rol du bang sgrom dang rdo rtsig stabs gang bde khru gang las mi dma' bas bskor /
NK003(ga)017:108: slob dpon gyi mdun du bdag bskyed kyi mchod pa dang /
NK003(ga)017:109: gzhan yang rol mo'i bye brag sogs 'og tu dgos pa'i yo byad rnams 'du bya /
NK003(ga)017:110: dngos gzhi bdag mdun gyi cho ga gzhung gsal ltar /
NK003(ga)017:111: cha gsum slob dpon gyi mdun du bshams nas re re bzhin 'bul ba las rgyun bzhag mi dgos /
NK003(ga)017:112: bkra shis skabs cho ga rgyas pa gzhan nas 'byung ba'i tshigs bcad tshang ma brjod na legs /
NK003(ga)017:113: 'od zer dri med skabs gang gi bang sgrom la
NK003(ga)017:114: kha chod bra barlinga can rgyab mchod rten yin na
NK003(ga)017:116: gang ltar yang lha sta gon gzhung bzhin legs par bya /
NK003(ga)017:117: de yi phyi nyin rdo leb la brkos pa'i dkyil 'khor bsham /
NK003(ga)017:118: de nas srog shing tshad ldan sbyang khrus byas pa
NK003(ga)017:119: rdo rje'i rwa rtse dbus kyi gdan gru bzhi la
NK003(ga)017:121: srog shing ljid na rdo leb kyis theg dka' bas
NK003(ga)017:122: phyi rol gyi khang sgrom dang bstun rdo rje'i rwa
NK003(ga)017:123: nas gdung mas 'degs pa sogs dkyil 'khor la chag
NK003(ga)017:125: dkyil 'khor gyi snam bu'i grwa bzhir dung chos dngos 'byor na rab /
NK003(ga)017:126: ma 'byor na rdo'am rdza las bcos sa dkar dang
NK003(ga)017:127: sra rtsi btang ba'i nang du lan tsh+wa dang dri
NK003(ga)017:129: shar gyi snam bu'i khar rdza phor lta bu'i nang du tsan+dana /
NK003(ga)017:131: shug pa sogs kyis bkang ba'i spos snod gsum /
NK003(ga)017:132: lho yi snam bur dri yi dung zhal gong smos lta bu dang /
NK003(ga)017:133: rdza phor lta bur me tog dang /
NK003(ga)017:135: nub kyi snam bur bum pa tshon rtsi can gyi nang du til nag /
NK003(ga)017:137: 'bras rnams bsres nas bcos pa'i thug pa kri sa ra zhes pas bkang ba dang /
NK003(ga)017:138: zas dkar gyis gang ba'i bum pa /
NK003(ga)017:139: rdza sder lta bur kham bu star ga rgun 'brum
NK003(ga)017:140: sogs shing tog sna tshogs kyi 'bras bu dgu bcu
NK003(ga)017:141: rtsa dgus bkang ba rnams bkod /
NK003(ga)017:142: gong gi sran ma ma sha ma rnyed na sran dkar gyis chog /
NK003(ga)017:143: byang gi snam bur rdza sder lta bur snum zan gyi gtor ma dkar zlum mthar /
NK003(ga)017:144: mar thud khur ba sogs kha zas sna tshogs kyis bskor ba dang /
NK003(ga)017:145: dri lngas bkang ba'i rdza bum kha rgyan mgul chings can /
NK003(ga)017:146: rdza sder lta bur spos dang me tog rnams bzhag /
NK003(ga)017:148: dri yi dung chos kyi rgyab tu /
NK003(ga)017:149: rdo'am shing zla gam la tshogs bdag gi sku glang
NK003(ga)017:150: gdong sngon po dgra s+t+wa dang la phug 'dzin pa
NK003(ga)017:151: tshon rtsi can gyi spyi steng du dngul lam /
NK003(ga)017:152: ma 'byor na zangs lta bu'i rin chen mar me bzhag cing gzer btab nas mi 'gul bar bya /
NK003(ga)017:153: de'i phyi rol du phyogs rer mchod pa tshar re dang /
NK003(ga)017:154: nub tu lhag gsum mam gcig /
NK003(ga)017:155: ma 'byor na lho nub nas brtsams te rdza phor lta bur mchod yon /
NK003(ga)017:159: zhal zas rnams sngar smos pa lta bu dang /
NK003(ga)017:160: rdza sder sogs su khur ba sna tshogs /
NK003(ga)017:163: 'o thug bskol ba'am phyur bas bkang ba dang /
NK003(ga)017:164: mar me bcas zlum bskor du bshams /
NK003(ga)017:165: de'i phyi rol du phyogs bzhir stegs bu'i khar mchod yon gyi dung chos bzed zhal bcas /
NK003(ga)017:166: de rnams kyi bar mtshams su spos mar me zhal zas rnams tshar re /
NK003(ga)017:167: de'i phyi rol phyogs mtshams brgyad du /
NK003(ga)017:168: tog leb mo'i ngos su rma bya'i mdongs sbyar ba'am /
NK003(ga)017:169: ma 'byor na bris pas kyang rung bas rgyal mtshan shar dkar /
NK003(ga)017:176: byang shar ljang ser rnams dang /
NK003(ga)017:177: bkra shis rdzas brgyad dngos rdzas 'byor na legs /
NK003(ga)017:178: ma 'byor na rdo leb zlum po chung ngu'am /
NK003(ga)017:179: gro ga lta bu la bris nas rgyal mtshan so so'i mgul du btags /
NK003(ga)017:180: de'i phyi rol nas ras dmar pos zlum por bskor /
NK003(ga)017:181: steng du srog shing las bang sgrom gyi phyogs bzhir
NK003(ga)017:182: ras skud bsgril ma lta bu brkyangs pa la dar
NK003(ga)017:183: gyi lda ldi ste dar dpyang dang /
NK003(ga)017:186: me tog gi chun po rnams gos dar las byas pas dpyangs /
NK003(ga)017:187: de nas cho ga gzhung ltar btang /
NK003(ga)017:188: skabs 'dir glegs bam bklag ces pa 'od zer dri
NK003(ga)017:189: med kyi gzungs dpon slob thams cad kyis grub na
NK003(ga)017:191: ma mtha' yang tshar re bklag dgos /
NK003(ga)017:192: spyir gzungs mdo klog mkhan zur du bzhag rgyu byung na yang legs /
NK003(ga)017:193: de nas srog shing gi cho ga'i skabs phyogs re
NK003(ga)017:194: re bzhin 'gor mchod pa byin rlabs nges par dgos
NK003(ga)017:195: / spro na mchod pa'i skabs rab 'byams rgya mtsho sogs tshigs bcad spel /
NK003(ga)017:196: gang ltar yang mchod pa'i sngags /
NK003(ga)017:197: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa pa ri w+aa ra
NK003(ga)017:198: ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha p+au dza me g+ha sa mu dra
NK003(ga)017:199: s+pha ra na sa ma ye +aahmh'u /
NK003(ga)017:200: de bzhin du pad+yam sogs sbyar ba'i mthar /
NK003(ga)017:201: rol mo dang bcas mchod pa'i sprin gyi sngags brjod /
NK003(ga)017:202: gtor ma byin rlabs cha gsum ltar bya /
NK003(ga)017:203: so so'i mjug tu phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK003(ga)017:204: che ba'i che mchog sogs mdo rgyud nas byung ba'i
NK003(ga)017:205: bkra shis sh+lo ka gsum lnga sogs gang 'os brjod
NK003(ga)017:206: / mjug tu shar sgo nas bkra shis skabs gtsug
NK003(ga)017:207: tor dri med kyi cho ga las byung ba'i bya
NK003(ga)017:208: rgyud kyi bkra shis ring mo dang /
NK003(ga)017:209: bzang spyod lta bu'i smon lam rgyas par bya'o //
NK003(ga)017:210: de nas bang ba'i khar shing leb sogs kyi kha gcod dam par rgyab /
NK003(ga)017:211: srog shing dang kha chod kyi mtshams sogs bye 'jim
NK003(ga)017:212: lta bu'i zhal ba byas nas nang du rdul sogs
NK003(ga)017:214: s+aats+tsha rang rang gi dkyil 'khor steng du 'jog dgos kyang shong dka' ba dang /
NK003(ga)017:215: bar mtshams bye ma sogs kyis bkang dgos stabs dkyil 'khor dang /
NK003(ga)017:216: yo byad chud zos su 'gro dogs na steng du
NK003(ga)017:217: bzhag kyang mi rung ba med pas gong gi kha
NK003(ga)017:218: chod steng du bang sgrom lta bu rim gyis bsgrigs
NK003(ga)017:219: pa dang bstun thog mar gtsug tor dri med s+aats+tsha
NK003(ga)017:222: de steng 'od zer dri med kyi s+aats+tsha gang 'grub dang /
NK003(ga)017:223: ma mtha' yang dgu bcu rtsa dgu las mi nyung ba bzhag /
NK003(ga)017:224: bar mtshams bye ma skam pos bkang ba sogs lag tshag shin tu dam par bya dgos /
NK003(ga)017:225: gzhan s+aats+tsha 'bum ther sogs mang po yod na khang
NK003(ga)017:226: brtsegs skabs dbus kyi bang sgrom dang khang pa'i bar
NK003(ga)017:227: du gru chad byas nas legs par bzhag /
NK003(ga)017:228: khang brtsegs steng ma yang s+aats+tshasa khengs par bya /
NK003(ga)017:229: ring bsrel rnam bzhis mtshon gzungs gzhug rigs phal cher
NK003(ga)017:230: yang rdo sgrom mam snod lta bu'i nang du bcug
NK003(ga)017:231: la bar mtshams la cha sogs kyis sbyar na chu
NK003(ga)017:232: mi 'gro bar byas te khang brtsegs steng ma'i dbus
NK003(ga)017:233: su bzhag / mchod rten yin na s+aats+tsha lhag ma rnams bum pa'i nang du gang shong bya /
NK003(ga)017:234: gzhan gzungs gzhug bzhag tshul sogs lag len spyi khyab ltar shes dgos /
NK003(ga)017:235: khang brtsegs la khang bu brtsegs pa steng ma bkab
NK003(ga)017:236: nas de steng tog mtshon byed tsam mam rgyal mtshan
NK003(ga)017:238: grub na chos 'khor rim pa bcu gsum gdugs tog dang bcas pa byas kyang legs //
NK003(ga)017:239: gong gi yo byad nyer mkho snga tshags dgos pa la /
NK003(ga)017:240: seng ldeng gi phur pa brgyad dam /
NK003(ga)017:241: ma 'byor na shug pa tsher ma can gyis kyang rung /
NK003(ga)017:248: shug pa rtsa rtse dang shar rtags ma nor ba'i srog shing /
NK003(ga)017:249: de la byug rgyu'i dri bzang /
NK003(ga)017:250: dkri dpyad ras ser sogs dgos 'dengs /
NK003(ga)017:251: srog shing gi gzungs kyis mtshon gzungs gzhug ring bsrel bzhi'am lnga'i rigs gang 'byor /
NK003(ga)017:252: 'od zer dri med kyi gzungs tshang ma /
NK003(ga)017:253: dri med rnam gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor //
NK003(ga)017:254: gtsug tor dri med la bla bre sngon po /
NK003(ga)017:255: mchod pa'i snod rdzas sogs kyi ting phor rgyas par nga lnga /
NK003(ga)017:267: gdugs rnams rgyas par re re nas so gnyis re /
NK003(ga)017:269: de rnams 'dzugs sa rdza yi spos 'dzin lta bu grangs mnyam dang sgab dkris dmar po /
NK003(ga)017:274: ting phor rgyas par nyer gsum /
NK003(ga)017:276: rdza sder rgyas par so gcig /
NK003(ga)017:288: srog shing gi phyogs bzhir brkyang rgyu'i ras skud /
NK003(ga)017:292: me tog chun po rnams bzhi re /
NK003(ga)017:302: rgun 'brum sogs shing tog sna tshogs /
NK003(ga)017:306: rma bya'i mdongs brgyad bcas dgos //
NK003(ga)017:309: tha ma stong phrag sogs cho ga'i sgo nas legs par bsgrubs /
NK003(ga)017:310: de nas slob dpon bsnyen pa song nas /
NK003(ga)017:311: sgrub grogs 1 dang bcas sa chog bya /
NK003(ga)017:312: de rjes khang brtsegs thog bkab pa'i bar tshar nas
NK003(ga)017:313: snga dro gtsug tor dri med kyi cho ga 2btang
NK003(ga)017:314: / de yi phyi dro 'od zer dri med kyi sta gon /
NK003(ga)017:315: de'i phyi nyin srog shing btsugs la 'od zer dri med kyi dngos gzhi srog shing 'dzugs chog bya /
NK003(ga)017:320: gzhan yang bstan pa'i spyi rim lta bu gal chen
NK003(ga)017:321: yin na sa chog tshar ma thag mchod rten gyi
NK003(ga)017:322: 'og tu dam sri mnan pa sogs tshad ldan bya
NK003(ga)017:324: tog gi nang du gdugs dkar 'khor lo bca' sgrub
NK003(ga)017:325: tshad ldan byas pa yod na rdza'i ga'u lta bur
NK003(ga)017:326: bzhag cing gdugs dkar gyi rgyal mtshan 'dzugs chog dang
NK003(ga)017:327: / des mtshon rgyal mtshan rtse mo'i gzungs glegs bam gyi tshul du bris pa bzhag cing /
NK003(ga)017:329: srog shing gi nang du shong na 'od zer dri
NK003(ga)017:330: med kyi gzungs tshang ma gser ram mtshal gyis bris
NK003(ga)017:333: dril tsha sa dang bcas bzhugs pa shin tu gal che /
NK003(ga)017:334: ma shong na rdza'i ga'u lta bur bcug nas srog shing la bcings kyang rung /
NK003(ga)017:335: de lta bu'i rten gyi bya ba mthar phyin nas rab gnas rgyas bsdus gang rung gis mnga' gsol /
NK003(ga)017:336: rgyun dang dus su phyag bskor mchod pa sogs bgyis
NK003(ga)017:337: pas dri med rnam gnyis kyi gzungs nas gsungs pas
NK003(ga)017:338: mtshon / phan yon bsam mi khyab pa 'thob cing
NK003(ga)017:339: 'phral dang yun gyi phan bde'i dge mtshan 'grub pa
NK003(ga)017:340: mtshon / ni nges pa'o // gzungs sngags yid bzhin nor bu'i cho ga'i tshul //
NK003(ga)017:341: nyer mkho'i gsal byed chu gos rtser bkod pa'i //
NK003(ga)017:342: legs bshad 'dis kyang mtha' yas yid can kun //
NK003(ga)017:343: thar bde'i dga' ston rtag tu rgyas gyur cig /
